docs.summary: An element for displaying headings on your [dashboard page](https://dev.wix.com/docs/build-apps/developer-tools/cli/wix-cli-for-apps/dashboard-pages).
description: The dashboard heading element is intended for use on
in your Wix site or in [Wix Blocks](https://support.wix.com/en/article/wix-blocks-check-out-our-articles),
but you may use it on any page.

docs.summary: A property that represents an element's custom CSS classes.
description: > **Note:** This standard element property is not relevant for DashboardHeading.
> For more information, see [Styling Elements with CSS](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w/styling-elements-with-css)

docs.summary: Sets or gets the text of a dashboard heading element.
description: Use the `text` property to set the content of the dashboard heading element. Any existing text is replaced.

examples.title: Set the dashboard heading's text to the specified value
